        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Five years ago, Min Hui pretended to be Xin Qi’s long-lost childhood friend to help him cope with the sudden death of his friend, while hiding her growing love for him. Xin Qi, suffering from a life-threatening heart condition, rejected her attempts to confess, and when the truth was finally revealed, he cut all ties with her.\n\nNow, five years later, they are reunited at a business event. Min Hui has become\n\nan R&D assistant, while Xin Qi is a successful CEO. Despite his lingering anger, Xin Qi soon learns that Min Hui has a son with the same heart condition he suffers from, leading him to realize he is the father. Through heartfelt conversations, explanations, and a quirky living arrangement, can they heal old wounds and rekindle their love as a family?",
            "source": "mydramalist",
            "source_link": "https://mydramalist.com/723145-the-love-you-give-me"
        },
